quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,10,"N’Umuremyi\twawe\tmugihe\tyahamagara\tintumwa\tyiwe\tMussa\t(iiii) amubwira ati:- nugende kuri barya bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  26,11,"Abantu bo kwa Fir’auni ubabwire uti:- mbega ntibatinya Imana"
  26,12,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje mu vy’ukuri jewe ndatinya yuko abo bantu bompakana"
  26,13,"N’igikiriza canje ntiki nyorohereza hamwe n’ururimi wanje ntirutomora amajambo neza, rero nushikirize ubu butumwa kwa mwene wanje Haruna (iii)"
  26,14,Nabo n’abantu bafise amakosa imbere yanje mugabo ntinya yuko bongandagura
  26,15,"Avuga ati:- Oya sivyo, ahubwo ni mugende n’ibi bitangaro vyanje, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi kumwe namwe kandi turabumva"
  26,16,"Rero nimugende kwa Fir’auni mumubwire muti:- ntankeka twebwe turi intumwa z’Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,17,Turungitswe yuko wobatwarira turi kumwe twese hamwe na bene Israeri
  26,18,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- mbega wewe ntitwakurereye iwacu muugihe wari ukiri mutoyi hanyuma turabana twese kumyaka myinshi y’ubuzima bwawe bwose"
  26,19,Kandi waragize ico gikorwa cawe muvyo wagize vyose uca uba mu bantu badashima
  26,20,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivuga iti:- naragize ivyo vyose ngaho mugihe nari mu bantu bazimiye"
  26,21,Rero nanje naciye ndabahunga mugihe natinya Umuremyi wanje ubu yarampaye amategeko kandi yarampezagiye ngombe ndi muntumwa z’Imana
  26,22,Kandi uwo niwo mugisha wangiriyeko impuhwe wukubashira mubuja wa bene Israeri
  26,23,"Fir’auni yavuze ati:- ni nde uyo Muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,24,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa ivuga iti :- n’Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo nimwaba mwebwe muri mu bantu mwemera"
  26,25,"Fir’aauni\tyabwiye\tabantu\tbamukikuje\tati :-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimwumva"
  26,26,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) aca avuga ati:- Umuremyi niwe muremyi w’abavyeyi banyu baho hambere"
  26,27,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- ntankeka iyo ntumwa yanyu yarungitswe kuri mwebwe n’umusazi"
  26,28,"Intumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tivuga\titi:-\tUmuremyi\tw’ubuseruko n’uburengera zuba hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo nimwaba mutegera neza"
  26,29,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- niwakurikira iyindi Mana atari jewe mu vy’ukuri nzokugira nk’abantu bari mwibohero"
  26,30,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivuga iti:- mbega naho nokuzanira ikintu kiri k’umugaragaro"
  26,31,"Fir’auni nawe amwishura ati:- nukizane niwaba uri mu bantu bavugisha ukuri kwama"
  26,32,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ijugunya inkoni yiwe, mukanya isase ica ihinduka inzoka nyakuri iri k’umugaragaro"
  26,33,Ica isokorora ukuboko kwayo mumpuzu mumwanya isase guca kurera derere kubantu bakubonye